        <li><a href="https://constitutioncenter.org/the-constitution/amendments/amendment-xxv" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-dem hover:underline">National Constitution Center: 25th Amendment</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://hls.harvard.edu/today/watergate-era-reforms-50-years-later/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-dem hover:underline">Harvard Law School: Watergate-Era Reforms, 50 Years Later</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://www.gao.gov/products/095406" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-dem hover:underline">GAO: Congressional Budget and Impoundment Control Act</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://campaignlegal.org/update/significance-firing-inspectors-general-explained" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-dem hover:underline">Campaign Legal Center: Significance of Firing Inspectors General</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://www.npr.org/2025/01/25/g-s1-44771/trump-fires-inspectors-general" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-dem hover:underline">NPR: Trump Fires Inspectors General</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://www.cbpp.org/research/federal-budget/new-data-show-trump-administrations-illegal-targeted-withholding-of-funds" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-dem hover:underline">CBPP: Trump Administration's Withholding of Funds</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://protectdemocracy.org/work/protecting-our-democracy-act-2/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-dem hover:underline">Protect Democracy: Protecting Our Democracy Act</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

  </section>
</Layout>
